<B>__{passes williamson and the u.n. security guy in the doorway.}
<A>__{drew sees them. uh, oh. the only thing she can do to make herself inconspicuous is to drop into the canadian rep's chair and turn her back on them like she's one of the assembly members. she sits up, shuffles the files around. glancing furtively to either side, she sees that everyone else is wearing the translation earphone. she puts one on.}
<B>__{angle on the detective}
