<D>__{this crisis falls at the feet of one nation and one nation only! canada!}
<B>__{all eyes turn to drew.}
<C>__{chinese rep}
<D>__{how do you defend such a position! the world is waiting to hear!}
<A>__{these are fighting words. the assembly grows silent. drew wishes she could beam herself somewhere off planet. she gulps air. glances left, right. but she knows the detective's eyes are on the back of her}
